ownable.ownings
Class Dog

java.lang.Object
  ownable.ownings.Ownable
      ownable.ownings.Dog

public class Dog
extends Ownable

A class of dogs as a special kind of ownable. In addition to a value and an owner, dogs have a name and a minimal amount of food they need every day.

Version:
2.0
Author:
Eric Steegmans
